<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title || 'Login' %> | ZimParks Platform</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/auth.css">
</head>
<body>
  <main class="auth-shell">
    <section class="auth-stage auth-stage--split">
      <aside class="auth-hero auth-hero--editorial">
        <div class="hero-topbar">
          <div class="auth-brand">
            <div class="brand-mark"><img src="/images/logo.png" alt="ZimParks logo"></div>
            <div>
              <h1>ZimParks</h1>
              <p>Central conservation operations platform</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/feedback/submit" class="ghost-link">Public feedback</a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-panel hero-panel--editorial">
          <span class="hero-eyebrow">Mission control</span>
          <h2>Coordinate parks.<br>Track field data.<br>Respond faster.</h2>
          <p>Inspired by the editorial structure of the Redan experience, adapted for a darker conservation-focused interface with stronger operational clarity.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/create-account" class="hero-action hero-action--light">Create account</a>
          <a href="/forgot-password" class="hero-action hero-action--outline">Recover access</a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-metric-grid">
          <div class="hero-metric">
            <span>Modules</span>
            <strong>8</strong>
            <p>Wildlife, alerts, environment, feedback, analytics, and more.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-metric">
            <span>Roles</span>
            <strong>5</strong>
            <p>Controlled dashboards for admin, ranger, tourism, analyst, and public.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-metric">
            <span>Security</span>
            <strong>OTP</strong>
            <p>Single-use verification and session-gated registration or reset.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-visual-card">
          <div class="visual-label-row">
            <span class="visual-label">ZimParks overview</span>
            <span class="visual-status">Dark green future-ready theme</span>
          </div>
          <div class="visual-window">
            <img src="/images/login-hero.png" alt="ZimParks parks operations" class="visual-hero-image">
            <div class="visual-orbit visual-orbit--one"></div>
            <div class="visual-orbit visual-orbit--two"></div>
            <div class="visual-grid"></div>
            <div class="visual-screen">
              <div class="visual-screen-label">National park operations</div>
              <div class="visual-screen-title">Protecting wildlife, tourism, and infrastructure across Zimbabwe.</div>
              <div class="visual-screen-copy">ZimParks coordinates conservation reporting, environmental monitoring, visitor services, infrastructure oversight, and alert response from one connected platform.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="visual-badge">LIVE UI CONCEPT</div>
          </div>
          <div class="visual-pill-row">
            <span class="hero-chip">Editorial hero</span>
            <span class="hero-chip">Glass panels</span>
            <span class="hero-chip">Operational layout</span>
            <span class="hero-chip">Future accents</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <section class="auth-card auth-card--login">
        <div class="login-card-top">
          <div class="login-brand-panel">
            <div class="login-brand-grid"></div>
            <div class="login-brand-image-wrap">
              <img src="/images/login-hero.png" alt="ZimParks parks operations" class="login-brand-image">
            </div>
            <div class="login-brand-copy">
              <span class="auth-kicker">ZimParks</span>
              <h2>Managing protected areas through one central platform.</h2>
              <p>ZimParks brings together field reporting, environmental tracking, alerts, tourism oversight, and operational visibility for stronger park management.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="login-brand-badge">ZimParks</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="login-form-shell">
          <div class="auth-card-header">
            <div>
              <span class="auth-kicker">Staff Sign-In</span>
              <h2>Login</h2>
              <p>Use your assigned email and password to access the role dashboard and operational workspace.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-badge">Secure Session</div>
          </div>

          <% if (successMessage) { %><div class="notice success"><%= successMessage %></div><% } %>
          <% if (message) { %><div class="notice info"><%= message %></div><% } %>
          <% if (errors && errors.length) { %>
            <div class="notice error">
              <ul>
                <% errors.forEach((error) => { %><li><%= error.msg %></li><% }) %>
              </ul>
            </div>
          <% } %>

          <form method="POST" action="/login" class="auth-form">
            <div class="field-grid">
              <div class="field-group">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input id="email" type="email" name="email" value="<%= formData.email || '' %>" placeholder="name@zimparks.co.zw" required>
              </div>
              <div class="field-group">
                <label for="password">Password</label>
                <input id="password" type="password" name="password" value="<%= formData.password || '' %>" placeholder="Enter your password" required>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="auth-form-actions">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary full-width">Login</button>
            </div>
          </form>

          <div class="card-divider"></div>

          <div class="auth-links">
            <a href="/create-account">Create account</a>
            <a href="/forgot-password">Forgot password</a>
            <a href="/feedback/submit">Public feedback</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
